name: Gangsta Goose
description:
A  working version of the game I originally made for GMTK GameJam 2022.

Still a little buggy but it's playable!

The game I submitted before was completely broken but I have since hopefully squashed most of the bugs. I know reuploading games is against the rules, but my original submission was literally unplayable so who cares, it wasn't going to win haha.

Literally, my first ever game dev project that I've actually kind of finished, it's not perfect by any means but at least you can shoot stuff.  I know it's not that fun to play but gets better the further you progress. Enjoy!

Thank you for the feedback and support.
